      "body" : "OK, I think Ive addressed every issue with this, except for the question of whether to popup before adding the recipient to the transaction or not until the send confirm dialog.  I am of the opinion that there shouldnt be an extra popup before adding as it will annoy users if you can create a desktop popup once per second (or any other time frame) from js.  I would instead just say that since the sendcoinsentry scrolls to the bottom when new recipients are added, it can be safely left up to the user to check the send (especially since the list of recipients is repeated in the confirmation dialog anyway).",
